HEADWORD: Polymnite
<hw>Pol"ym*nite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ full of
moss; <grk>poly`s</grk> much + <?/ moss.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A
